# 🧠 AI Resume Screening Chatbot

An AI-powered recruiter assistant that analyzes and shortlists candidates from multiple resumes using NLP and semantic search.

## 🚀 Features
- Upload multiple resumes (PDF)
- Extract skills and experience
- Semantic search using embeddings
- Candidate ranking with match score
- Chat-based querying interface

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- Streamlit
- LangChain (RAG)
- FAISS
- HuggingFace Embeddings
- Groq LLaMA 3.1

## 🧠 Architecture
1. Upload resumes
2. Extract text from PDFs
3. Split into chunks
4. Convert into embeddings
5. Store in FAISS vector database
6. Retrieve relevant chunks based on query
7. Generate response using LLM

## 🌐 Live Demo
https://rag-chatbot-mjuv6w8amagwrhzfrjdxcj.streamlit.app/

